1
00:00:00,083 --> 00:00:02,208
Since my release, I’ve been trying

2
00:00:02,708 --> 00:00:05,500
To escape the area completely

3
00:00:05,666 --> 00:00:07,208
I was in a very difficult mental state

4
00:00:08,333 --> 00:00:11,208
I remained affected until ISIS left the area

5
00:00:11,458 --> 00:00:13,708
Of course, I didn’t wait for them

6
00:00:13,833 --> 00:00:15,083
I was the one who fled

7
00:00:15,500 --> 00:00:18,166
To the town of al-Bab in Rural Aleppo

8
00:00:19,666 --> 00:00:22,416
Because I couldn’t bear staying

9
00:00:22,666 --> 00:00:30,125
Even though I stayed away from the
city and avoided any contact with them

10
00:00:30,791 --> 00:00:32,583
Because of my terrible psychological state

11
00:00:33,041 --> 00:00:35,041
Once, I went down to my city

12
00:00:35,125 --> 00:00:37,541
And saw a man killed and crucified

13
00:00:38,250 --> 00:00:42,458
He was wearing an orange jumpsuit and was an elderly man

14
00:00:42,875 --> 00:00:44,708
Not younger than 50 years old

15
00:00:45,125 --> 00:00:47,416
That sight completely destroyed me

16
00:00:47,583 --> 00:00:51,041
And pushed me to leave the area for good

17
00:00:51,208 --> 00:00:52,708
I left by God’s grace

18
00:00:52,916 --> 00:00:54,000
And I didn’t return until after they had left

19
00:00:54,083 --> 00:00:56,666
When the Syrian Democratic Forces took control of the area
